    <item>
      <title>美国将宣布向乌克兰提供价值 7.25 亿美元的新武器计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/us-to-announce-725-million-arms-package-for-ukraine-including-mines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两名官员透露，美国即将宣布向乌克兰提供最新一批武器，这些武器均来自美国库存，总额约为 7.25 亿美元，其中包括总统乔·拜登批准的第二批杀伤人员地雷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/us-to-announce-725-million-arms-package-for-ukraine-including-mines</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 16:24:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚重返欧洲债券市场，发行 22 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/nigeria-s-latest-eurobond-sale-should-see-solid-demand-says-rmb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，尼日利亚两年多来首次发行欧洲债券，吸引了强劲的投资者需求，这使得政府能够收紧 22 亿美元债券的定价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/nigeria-s-latest-eurobond-sale-should-see-solid-demand-says-rmb</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 11:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将美元武器化被视为对金砖国家的无谓挑衅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/trump-weaponizing-dollar-seen-as-a-needless-brics-provocation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场观察人士表示，唐纳德·特朗普向世界各国施加新压力，要求其维持以美元为基础的金融体系，这种策略可能会适得其反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/trump-weaponizing-dollar-seen-as-a-needless-brics-provocation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:46:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
